CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 2, 1957, pg. 2, reads: "Modern Apt. - This is the entrance to the new, modern, apartment building next door to the two double large-family structures on Western Ave. Rest of block and most of area is strictly ultra-modern commercial, however. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Modern apartment building with diamond patterned brick work next to dilapidated multi-family brick building, Western Avenue, Northside
